dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Milwaukee County, WI 2025
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2025 and includes the layers 'MILWAUKEE_ROADS_2025' and 'MILWAUKEE_ROW_2025'. [Roads: Street Centerlines with Address Ranges and Highway Designations, Milwaukee County, WI. ROW: right-of-way boundary lines covering Milwaukee County, Wisconsin]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
